lry, and diamonds. We are a venture-backed, high-growth business that offers competitive compensation in a creative, flexible environment that invests in its professionals.",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":65,"children":66},{},[67],{"type":39,"value":68},"This position reports to the VP of Engineering. Vivrelle is headquartered in New York City, but this role can be fully remote.",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":70,"children":71},{},[72],{"type":39,"value":73},"Your responsibilities will include:\n● Plan, execute, monitor, track and report on technology projects using Agile development processes & techniques.\n● Develop project plans and schedules, including scope, resources, budgets, and timelines.\n● Coordinate the efforts of cross-functional teams, including software developers, quality assurance, and product management\n● Monitor and report on project progress, including status updates and risk management.\n● Facilitate communication between team members, stakeholders, and clients.\n● Ensure that all project deliverables meet the required quality standards and are completed on time.\n● Conduct project reviews and retrospectives to identify lessons learned and opportunities for improvement.\n● Manage agile sprint cycles - Scrum Master, grooming, sprint planning and retrospectives.\n● Document current processes and pushing the business forward by defining new processes with an eye for efficiency.\n● KPI definition, tracking and reporting.\n● JIRA management.\n● Engineering calendar management.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":75,"children":77},{"id":76},"whats-in-it-for-you",[78],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":79,"children":80},{},[81],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":82,"children":83},{},[84],{"type":39,"value":85},"What’s in it for you",{"type":25,"tag":87,"props":88,"children":89},"ol",{},[90,96,101,106,111],{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":92,"children":93},"li",{},[94],{"type":39,"value":95},"Learn and evolve your skills using the latest and greatest technology tools in a rapidly growing company.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":97,"children":98},{},[99],{"type":39,"value":100},"Learn from the best engineers. We constantly challenge the status quo and invent new ways of building a great product.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":102,"children":103},{},[104],{"type":39,"value":105},"Flexible hours. Just join daily standups, sprint planning, and retrospective meetings. Other than that you’re in control of your own schedule.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":107,"children":108},{},[109],{"type":39,"value":110},"100% remote. Work anywhere, whether it is remotely in the comfort of your home, in a shared co-working space, in an RV on the beach, or while being a nomad in another country.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":112,"children":113},{},[114],{"type":39,"value":115},"Work on challenging problems, innovate, impacting lots of people's lives for the better while having fun doing it.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":117,"children":119},{"id":118},"required-qualifications",[120],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":121,"children":122},{},[123],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":124,"children":125},{},[126],{"type":39,"value":127},"Required Qualifications",{"type":25,"tag":87,"props":129,"children":130},{},[131,136,141,146,151,156,161,166,171],{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":132,"children":133},{},[134],{"type":39,"value":135},"5+ years of full-time hands-on Project Management experience.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":137,"children":138},{},[139],{"type":39,"value":140},"Upper-intermediate to fluent speaking and writing English. Able to have a real-time conversation.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":142,"children":143},{},[144],{"type":39,"value":145},"Jira usage and administration experience.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":147,"children":148},{},[149],{"type":39,"value":150},"Experience running SCRUM ceremonies.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":152,"children":153},{},[154],{"type":39,"value":155},"Understanding of basic software engineering language and concepts.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":157,"children":158},{},[159],{"type":39,"value":160},"Experience defining and tracking KPIs for agile engineering teams.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":162,"children":163},{},[164],{"type":39,"value":165},"Experience managing cross functional projects (between Marketing, Engineering, Operations, etc).",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":167,"children":168},{},[169],{"type":39,"value":170},"Detail oriented and organized.",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":172,"children":173},{},[174],{"type":39,"value":175},"Experience with note taking during meetings.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":177,"children":179},{"id":178},"nice-to-haves",[180],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":181,"children":182},{},[183],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":184,"children":185},{},[186],{"type":39,"value":187},"Nice to haves",{"type":25,"tag":87,"props":189,"children":190},{},[191,196],{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":192,"children":193},{},[194],{"type":39,"value":195},"Experience administering vendors (managing contract renewal schedule, etc).",{"type":25,"tag":91,"props":197,"children":198},{},[199],{"type":39,"value":200},"Experience with interview scheduling.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":202,"children":204},{"id":203},"frequently-asked-questions",[205],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":206,"children":207},{},[208],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":209,"children":210},{},[211],{"type":39,"value":212},"Frequently Asked Questions",{"type":25,"tag":214,"props":215,"children":216},"blockquote",{},[217],{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":218,"children":219},{},[220],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":221,"children":222},{},[223],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":224,"children":225},{},[226],{"type":39,"value":227},"What are your typical clients?",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":229,"children":230},{},[231],{"type":39,"value":232},"The majority of our clients are venture-backed startups in the growth stage. Usually, at this stage, the company already achieved a product-market fit and is looking to expand rapidly. That’s where we bring the best engineering practices, strong architecture, and the latest technologies to help companies scale.",{"type":25,"tag":214,"props":234,"children":235},{},[236],{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":237,"children":238},{},[239],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":240,"children":241},{},[242],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":243,"children":244},{},[245],{"type":39,"value":246},"What is the length of your engagements?",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":248,"children":249},{},[250],{"type":39,"value":251},"Most of our long-term full-time engagements last multiple years so you are able to grow your career with the company you are currently working in.",{"type":25,"tag":214,"props":253,"children":254},{},[255],{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":256,"children":257},{},[258],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":259,"children":260},{},[261],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":262,"children":263},{},[264],{"type":39,"value":265},"What’s your company size?",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":267,"children":268},{},[269],{"type":39,"value":270},"The Right Balance team is 60+ engineers going to 200+ by the end of 2023. The current client size team is 50 people. It’s exciting to be a part of the solid engineering team making meaningful contributions.",{"type":25,"tag":214,"props":272,"children":273},{},[274],{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":275,"children":276},{},[277],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":278,"children":279},{},[280],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":281,"children":282},{},[283],{"type":39,"value":284},"What happens if the engagement is completed?",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":286,"children":287},{},[288],{"type":39,"value":289},"Most of our engagements are long-term in nature. That said, if the current engagement is ramping down, we’ll present you with more long-term opportunities to transition into.",{"type":25,"tag":214,"props":291,"children":292},{},[293],{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":294,"children":295},{},[296],{"type":25,"tag":31,"props":297,"children":298},{},[299],{"type":25,"tag":35,"props":300,"children":301},{},[302],{"type":39,"value":303},"What are your core values?